    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，我先确认一下结构。用户通过SchedulerApp发起请求，然后SA分别和Event、Reminder交互，这两个实体再各自访问DAO层和Service层，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SchedulerApp",
