    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的。另外安全方面需要特别注意：创建Event和Reminder时用Security_Firewall，数据持久化和调度时用Security_OAuth2，查询操作要用Security_ZeroTrust。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Security_Firewall",
        "Security_OAuth2",
        "Security_ZeroTrust"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先画出主干流程。User发Request add event给SchedulerApp，SA创建Event并带上Security_Firewall，然后Event调用EventDAO的add_event方法，带上Security_OAuth2。",
      "elements_involved": [
